        <p class="bento-desc">The agent ranking #1 for "moving to [your city]" publishes 3–4 blog posts per week about local neighborhoods, market trends, and buying advice. Between showings, closings, open houses, and client calls, no agent has time to write that content. theStacc does it automatically — 30 neighborhood-focused articles per month (cost of living guides, market reports, school district breakdowns) plus 30 GBP posts. Zero writing from you. First article live in 24 hours.</p>
        <ul class="bento-list">
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>30 neighborhood/real estate articles/month — auto-published to your site</li>
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>30 GBP posts/month — market updates, open houses, neighborhood highlights</li>
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Topics Zillow can't write: "best neighborhoods in [city] for families"</li>
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>$1 trial · No contract · Cancel anytime</li>
