          <p class="ba-sub">For agents or brokerages that want keyword research, rank tracking, and competitor analysis in one affordable platform.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">SE Ranking gives real estate professionals a complete SEO research toolkit at half the price of Semrush. For an agent wanting to understand what competing realtors rank for, SE Ranking's competitor analysis is genuinely useful — it shows what keywords any domain ranks for, their traffic estimates, and their backlink profile. The local SEO add-on handles listing management and local rank tracking. Enter a competitor's URL and see every keyword they rank for in your market. That's your content roadmap.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
