          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">01</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Ask which lane you're competing in — listing searches belong to Zillow, neighborhood content belongs to you</h4>
              <p>No SEO tool helps you outrank Zillow on "homes for sale in [city]." But any tool that publishes consistent neighborhood content can help you own "best neighborhoods in [city] for families." Know your lane before buying your tools.</p>
